#: ../../source/usage/configure_sensor.md:1
msgid "Configure Sensors for the robot"
msgstr "为机器人配置传感器"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_sensor.md:3
msgid ""
"Robots can carry sensors for environment perception. IR-SIM provides a 2D"
" LiDAR (`lidar2d`) and a simplified 2D FMCW LiDAR (`fmcw_lidar2d`, with "
"per-beam radial velocity), plus an optional field-of-view (FOV) region; "
"all are attached per object in the YAML file. This page shows how to "
"configure them and tune noise."
msgstr ""
"机器人可以携带传感器进行环境感知。IR-SIM 提供 2D 激光雷达（`lidar2d`）以及简化的 2D FMCW "
"激光雷达（`fmcw_lidar2d`，每条光束附带径向速度），以及可选的视场（FOV）区域；它们都在 YAML "
"文件中按对象进行配置。本页展示如何配置它们并调节噪声。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_sensor.md:5
msgid "LiDAR Configuration Parameters"
msgstr "LiDAR 配置参数"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_sensor.md:7
msgid ""
"The YAML configuration file and Python Script below shows an example of a"
" robot with a 2D LiDAR sensor:"
msgstr "下面的 YAML 配置与 Python 脚本展示了带 2D LiDAR 传感器的机器人示例："

#: ../../source/usage/configure_sensor.md
msgid "Python Script"
msgstr "Python 脚本"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_sensor.md
msgid "YAML Configuration"
msgstr "YAML 配置"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_sensor.md:33
msgid "YAML file (same name as the python script):"
msgstr "与 Python 脚本同名的 YAML 文件："

#: ../../source/usage/configure_sensor.md
msgid "Demonstration"
msgstr "演示"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_sensor.md:70
#: ../../source/usage/configure_sensor.md:336
msgid "Select Parameters"
msgstr "参数选择"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_sensor.md:79
msgid "Update order"
msgstr "更新顺序"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_sensor.md:81
msgid ""
"The environment updates sensors after all objects have moved in a step. "
"This avoids temporal skew in readings. If you control objects manually, "
"either pass `sensor_step=True` to `ObjectBase.step(...)` or call "
"`obj.sensor_step()` after updating object states."
msgstr ""
"环境会在所有对象完成该时间步移动后再更新传感器，从而避免读数的时间偏差。若手动控制对象，请在 `ObjectBase.step(...)` 中传入"
" `sensor_step=True`，或在更新对象状态后调用 `obj.sensor_step()`。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_sensor.md:84
msgid "Important Parameters Explained"
msgstr "关键参数说明"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_sensor.md:86
msgid ""
"To configure the 2D LiDAR sensor, the sensor name of `lidar2d` should be "
"defined in the `sensors` section of the robot. Key parameters of the "
"LiDAR sensor are explained below:"
msgstr "若要配置 2D LiDAR，需在机器人 `sensors` 部分定义名为 `lidar2d` 的传感器。主要参数如下："

#: ../../source/usage/configure_sensor.md:88
msgid "**range_min**: The minimum range of the laser beam."
msgstr "**range_min**：激光束的最小量程。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_sensor.md:89
msgid "**range_max**: The maximum range of the laser beam."
msgstr "**range_max**：激光束的最大量程。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_sensor.md:90
msgid "**angle_range**: The angle range of the laser beam."
msgstr "**angle_range**：激光束覆盖的角度范围。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_sensor.md:91
msgid "**number**: The number of beams."
msgstr "**number**：束数量。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_sensor.md:92
msgid "**alpha**: The transparency of the laser beam."
msgstr "**alpha**：激光束透明度。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_sensor.md:94
msgid ""
"A full list of parameters can be found in the [YAML "
"Configuration](../yaml_config/configuration.md)."
msgstr "完整参数列表见 [YAML 配置](../yaml_config/configuration.md)。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_sensor.md:97
msgid "Advanced Lidar Configuration with noise"
msgstr "带噪声的高级 LiDAR 配置"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_sensor.md:99
msgid ""
"To add noise to the LiDAR sensor, you can set the `noise` parameter to "
"`True`."
msgstr "若需为 LiDAR 添加噪声，可将 `noise` 设为 `True`。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_sensor.md:163
msgid "LiDAR scan with Gaussian noise"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/usage/configure_sensor.md:172
msgid ""
"Gaussian noise is added to the LiDAR sensor with the `std` and "
"`angle_std` parameters. The `std` parameter is the standard deviation of "
"the range noise, and the `angle_std` parameter is the standard deviation "
"of the angle noise."
msgstr ""
"通过 `std` 与 `angle_std` 参数为 LiDAR 添加高斯噪声。其中 `std` 为距离噪声的标准差，`angle_std` "
"为角度噪声的标准差。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_sensor.md:174
msgid "FMCW LiDAR Configuration Parameters"
msgstr "FMCW 激光雷达配置参数"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_sensor.md:176
msgid ""
"IR-SIM also provides a simplified 2D FMCW LiDAR sensor named "
"`fmcw_lidar2d`. It keeps the same beam geometry as the standard 2D LiDAR,"
" but each valid beam additionally reports a scalar `radial_velocity` "
"measurement. This makes it useful for demonstrating how Doppler "
"measurements can help interpret dynamic obstacles."
msgstr ""
"IR-SIM 还提供了一个简化的 2D FMCW 激光雷达传感器，名为 `fmcw_lidar2d`。它保持与标准 2D "
"激光雷达相同的光束几何结构，但每条有效光束会额外返回一个标量 "
"`radial_velocity`（径向速度）测量值。这便于演示多普勒测量如何帮助理解动态障碍物。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_sensor.md:178
msgid ""
"The example below uses a stationary ego sensor with a forward 120-degree "
"field of view and multiple moving obstacles. When plotting is enabled, "
"valid returns are colorized by radial velocity and marked at their "
"endpoints."
msgstr "下方示例使用一个静止的传感器主体，朝前方覆盖 120 度视场，并设置了多个移动障碍物。开启绘图后，有效回波会按径向速度着色，并在端点处标记出来。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_sensor.md:241
msgid "Key FMCW-specific parameters are:"
msgstr "FMCW 专用关键参数："

#: ../../source/usage/configure_sensor.md:243
msgid ""
"**motion_compensate**: Whether to remove ego-motion from the measured "
"radial velocity."
msgstr "**motion_compensate**：是否从测量的径向速度中扣除自身运动分量。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_sensor.md:244
msgid ""
"**velocity_noise_std**: Standard deviation of Gaussian noise applied to "
"`radial_velocity`."
msgstr "**velocity_noise_std**：施加在 `radial_velocity` 上的高斯噪声标准差。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_sensor.md:246
msgid ""
"Visualization parameters live under the sensor's **`plot:`** sub-dict "
"(consistent with `lidar2d` and object `plot:`); flat top-level keys are "
"still accepted for backward compatibility:"
msgstr ""
"可视化参数位于传感器的 **`plot:`** 子字典下（与 `lidar2d` 及对象的 `plot:` "
"一致）；为保持向后兼容，扁平的顶层键仍然被接受："

#: ../../source/usage/configure_sensor.md:248
msgid ""
"**velocity_color**: Whether to colorize valid beams by radial velocity "
"during plotting."
msgstr "**velocity_color**：绘图时是否按径向速度对有效光束着色。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_sensor.md:249
msgid ""
"**velocity_color_max**: Velocity magnitude where the plotting color "
"saturates."
msgstr "**velocity_color_max**：绘图颜色达到饱和的速度幅值。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_sensor.md:251
msgid "The returned scan keeps the standard LiDAR angle metadata and adds:"
msgstr "返回的扫描数据保留了标准激光雷达的角度元数据，并新增以下字段："

#: ../../source/usage/configure_sensor.md:253
msgid "**radial_velocity**: Scalar radial velocity for each beam."
msgstr "**radial_velocity**：每条光束的标量径向速度。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_sensor.md:254
msgid "**valid**: Whether the beam has a valid return within `range_max`."
msgstr "**valid**：该光束是否在 `range_max` 范围内有有效回波。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_sensor.md:256
msgid ""
"The complete runnable example is available under "
"`usage/22fmcw_lidar_world/`."
msgstr "完整可运行示例位于 `usage/22fmcw_lidar_world/`。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_sensor.md:259
msgid "FOV Configuration Parameters"
msgstr "视场（FOV）配置参数"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_sensor.md:261
msgid ""
"The YAML configuration file and Python Script below shows an example of "
"objects within the field of view (FOV). The FOV is defined by the `fov` "
"(float) and `fov_radius` (float) parameters in the object configuration. "
"Each object has a FOV that can detect the robot within the FOV by the "
"function `fov_detect_object()`."
msgstr ""
"下方的 YAML 配置与 Python 脚本展示了 FOV 中的对象示例。FOV 由对象配置中的 `fov`（角度）与 "
"`fov_radius`（半径）参数定义。每个对象都拥有 FOV，可通过 `fov_detect_object()` 检测视场内的机器人。"

